maple-unpack-native
===================

This crate is a Rust port of the dynamic unpacking logic of unlicense by
Erwan Grelet (ergrelet), licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0.

  Upstream: https://github.com/ergrelet/unlicense
  License:  GPL-3.0

Ported components:
  - The driver and orchestration (application.py, frida_exec.py, winlicense3.py).
  - The import-wrapper emulation (emulation.py) and IAT scanning (imports.py).
  - The instrumentation agent at src/resources/agent.js is a verbatim copy of
    unlicense's resources/frida.js.

The dump-and-rebuild step that unlicense delegates to Scylla (pyscylla) is not a
port of Scylla; it is an independent native PE reconstruction (src/pe_build.rs).

Because this crate derives from GPL-3.0 code, MapleDumper-rs is distributed under
the GNU General Public License v3.0. See the repository LICENSE.
